&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Core Experience&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years’ experience in Commercial/Industrial operations and maintenance (O&amp;amp;M) on solar power plants is preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Preventative Maintenance experience on Solar Utility equipment is preferred.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Candidates should possess strong mechanical and electrical experience with troubleshooting and installation skills.&lt;/li&gt;
