&lt;p data-start=&quot;752&quot; data-end=&quot;949&quot;&gt;This is a dynamic role that requires strong field and design experience, organizational skills, and the ability to balance technical work with permitting, reporting, and cross-team collaboration.&lt;/p&gt;
